  "title": "循環設計家飾品牌 by Saiens ",
  "date": "2025-06-04",
  "excerpt": "<p style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;\" data-rte-preserve-empty=\"true\"><strong>以帝雉石打造的by Saiens，讓材料美學進入日常家飾。</strong></p>",
