x;\"\n        >\n          \n        \n        \n\n        \n          \n            \n          <div\n              \n              \n              class=\"image-block-wrapper\"\n              data-animation-role=\"image\"\n              \n  \n\n          >\n            <div data-sqsp-image-classic-block-image-container class=\"sqs-image-shape-container-element\n              \n          \n        \n              \n            \" style=\"\n                position: relative;\n                \n                  padding-bottom:66.650390625%;\n                \n                overflow: hidden;-webkit-mask-image: -webkit-radial-gradient(white, black);\n              \"\n              >\n                \n                \n                \n                \n                \n                \n                \n                <img data-stretch=\"false\" data-src=\"/images/1752483347132-QU5JEH1QGPJR9UVNVV4K/by+saiens___.jpg\" data-image=\"/images/1752483347132-QU5JEH1QGPJR9UVNVV4K/by+saiens___.jpg\" data-image-dimensions=\"2048x1365\" data-image-focal-point=\"0.5,0.5\" alt=\"\" data-load=\"false\" elementtiming=\"system-image-block\" data-sqsp-image-classic-block-image src=\"/images/1752483347132-QU5JEH1QGPJR9UVNVV4K/by+saiens___.jpg\" width=\"2048\" height=\"1365\" alt=\"\" sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, (max-width: 767px) 100vw, 100vw\" style=\"display:block;object-fit: cover; width: 100%; height: 100%; object-position: 50% 50%\" onload=\"this.classList.add(&quot;loaded&quot;)\" srcset=\"/images/1752483347132-QU5JEH1QGPJR9UVNVV4K/by+saiens___.jpg 100w, /images/1752483347132-QU5JEH1QGPJR9UVNVV4K/by+saiens___.jpg 300w, /images/1752483347132-QU5JEH1QGPJR9UVNVV4K/by+saiens___.jpg 500w, /images/1752483347132-QU5JEH1QGPJR9UVNVV4K/by+saiens___.jpg 750w, /images/1752483347132-QU5JEH1QGPJR9UVNVV4K/by+saiens___.jpg 1000w, /images/1752483347132-QU5JEH1QGPJR9UVNVV4K/by+saiens___.jpg 1500w, /images/1752483347132-QU5JEH1QGPJR9UVNVV4K/by+saiens___.jpg 2500w\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-loader=\"sqs\">\n\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        \n          \n        \n\n        \n      \n        </figure>\n      \n\n    </div>\n  \n\n\n  \n\n\n</div></div><div class=\"sqs-block website-component-block sqs-block-website-component sqs-block-html html-block\" data-block-css=\"[&quot;https://definitions.sqspcdn.com/website-component-definition/static-assets/website.components.html/d92a980d-b660-49d1-a8a9-d817239fa29e_741/website.components.html.styles.css&quot;]\" data-block-scripts=\"[&quot;https://definitions.sqspcdn.com/website-component-definition/static-assets/website.components.html/d92a980d-b660-49d1-a8a9-d817239fa29e_741/website.components.html.visitor.js&quot;]\" data-block-type=\"1337\" data-definition-name=\"website.components.html\" data-sqsp-block=\"text\" data-website-component-id=\"9b702aa381df1b8f8e61\" id=\"block-9b702aa381df1b8f8e61\"><div class=\"sqs-block-content\"><div class=\"sqs-text-block-container\">\n  \n  <div class=\"sqs-html-content\" data-sqsp-text-block-content><pre><code>「Artistry meets Technology.&nbsp;當美學遇見科學。」</code></pre><pre><code>「透過減法設計的哲思，讓設計語彙在轉角、收編、結構比例的細節處表達，提供純萃、回歸本質的生活想像，也呼應&nbsp;by Saiens&nbsp;作為副產品的謙遜、內斂品牌精神，希望藉此能夠為每個人創造出家中最療癒、長久不變的寧靜角落。」</code></pre><p class=\"\" data-rte-preserve-empty=\"true\" style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;\"></p><h4 style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;\"><strong>質感人造石英石家飾品牌的誕生契機</strong></h4><pre><code>以大面積石英石板為主要核心產品及服務的&nbsp;Saiens，無論是&nbsp;Mikado Quartz&nbsp;帝雉石或&nbsp;Quartz&nbsp;闊石與空間設計專案配合時，難免有餘料的產生，經設計師的詢問，是否能夠將檯面切割下的小塊板材作為砧板，啟發了Michael&nbsp;對於家飾品牌的想像，也因而於&nbsp;2021&nbsp;年聖誕夜開始有了&nbsp;by Saiens&nbsp;的雛形。成立的契機其實說來偶然，然而卻也如同找到了最後一塊拼圖一般，完整了&nbsp;Saiens&nbsp;的企業&nbsp;DNA：對外擁有了除了石英石板材產品之外的質感家具、家飾副產品，對內則提供了活化庫存、餘料倉儲與清運的問題解決之道。因此，循環設計家飾品牌&nbsp;by Saiens&nbsp;就此誕生。 &nbsp;</code></pre><pre><code>參考全球新興家飾品牌的氛圍，如澳洲的&nbsp;En gold、瑞典&nbsp;Muuto&nbsp;或丹麥&nbsp;HAY，by Saiens&nbsp;試圖創造出由原料材質與設計都出自台灣的質感家具，目前以餐桌、邊几為核心產品，透過減法設計的哲思，讓設計語彙在轉角、收編、結構比例的細節處表達，提供純萃、回歸本質的生活想像，也呼應&nbsp;by Saiens&nbsp;作為副產品的謙遜、內斂品牌精神，希望藉此能夠為每個人創造出家中最療癒、長久不變的寧靜角落。</code></pre></div>\n\n\n  \n<style id=\"container-styles\">#block-9b702aa381df1b8f8e61 {\n    \n    --stroke-style: none;--stroke-thickness: 6px;\n    \n      \n      \n      \n    \n\n--tweak-text-block-background-color: initial;\n\n  }\n\n  #block-9b702aa381df1b8f8e61 .sqs-html-content {\n    \n    --tweak-text-block-padding: 6% 6% 6% 6%;\n  --tweak-text-block-padding: initial;\n}\n\n  #block-9b702aa381df1b8f8e61 {\n      mix-blend-mode: var(--tweak-text-block-blend\n  );\n      border-radius: var(--tweak-text-block-radius);\n  }\n\n  \n  \n#block-9b702aa381df1b8f8e61 {\n      --tweak-text-block-radius: 0px 0px 0px 0px;\n    }\n\n\n  \n  \n\n  #block-9b702aa381df1b8f8e61 {\n    }\n\n</style>\n\n<style id=\"override-container-styles\">\n    @media screen and (max-width: 767px) {\n          \n            \n\n#block-9b702aa381df1b8f8e61 {\n            \n            }\n        }\n    \n  \n    @media screen and (max-width: 767px) {\n          #block-9b702aa381df1b8f8e61 .sqs-html-content {\n            \n            }\n        }\n    \n  @media screen and (max-width: 767px) {\n          \n          \n\n          \n          \n          \n        }</style>\n\n<style class=\"transform-overrides-vars\">\n    \n  </style>\n\n\n\n</div>\n</div></div><div class=\"sqs-block website-component-block sqs-block-website-component sqs-block-spacer spacer-block sized vsize-1\" data-block-css=\"[&quot;https://definitions.sqspcdn.com/website-component-definition/static-assets/website.components.spacer/523604b1-74b7-4792-97e8-b24d3d8ea8c8_1064/website.components.spacer.styles.css&quot;]\" data-block-scripts=\"[&quot;https://definitions.sqspcdn.com/website-component-definition/static-assets/website.components.spacer/523604b1-74b7-4792-97e8-b24d3d8ea8c8_1064/website.components.spacer.visitor.js&quot;]\" data-block-type=\"1337\" data-definition-name=\"website.components.spacer\" data-website-component-id=\"c4e83d391be104a675e3\" id=\"block-c4e83d391be104a675e3\"><div class=\"sqs-block-content\">&nbsp;</div></div><div class=\"sqs-block website-component-block sqs-block-website-component sqs-block-html html-block\" data-block-css=\"[&quot;https://definitions.sqspcdn.com/website-component-definition/static-assets/website.components.html/d92a980d-b660-49d1-a8a9-d817239fa29e_741/website.components.html.styles.css&quot;]\" data-block-scripts=\"[&quot;https://definitions.sqspcdn.com/website-component-definition/static-assets/website.components.html/d92a980d-b660-49d1-a8a9-d817239fa29e_741/website.components.html.visitor.js&quot;]\" data-block-type=\"1337\" data-definition-name=\"website.components.html\" data-sqsp-block=\"text\" data-website-component-id=\"c7877b3e4dbd62b79bd5\" id=\"block-c7877b3e4dbd62b79bd5\"><div class=\"sqs-block-content\"><div class=\"sqs-text-block-container\">\n  \n  <div class=\"sqs-html-content\" data-sqsp-text-block-content><h4 style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;\"><strong>創造最科技也精品的氛圍與設計質感</strong></h4><pre><code>有著眾多讓人印象深刻的石英石花色，配合目前提供的&nbsp;20&nbsp;多種木質或金屬鐵件桌腳設計，便可誕生出成千上百種獨一無二的設計家飾。值得一提的是，by Saiens&nbsp;的家飾設計商業模式相當特別，具有介於成品的優勢與訂製傢俱的彈性：當顧客提出對於家飾的需求時，by Saiens&nbsp;的人員將進一步了解顧客對於家飾的期望用途、擺放的空間大小等等細節，接著根據顧客對於材質的偏好與氛圍想像，進一步推薦合適的石英石花紋、桌腳材質等，製出最適合顧客家中的家飾。 &nbsp;</code></pre><pre><code>不僅透過美學為顧客居家創造美好生活，by Saiens&nbsp;針對物理科學上的實用性與經濟成本也有著務實的考量。Mikado Quartz&nbsp;帝雉石板材最大的優勢就在於不吃色及耐刮的硬度，因此作為家飾品，使用上也能夠相當自在，喝酒、咖啡聚餐的污漬、孩子於上頭作畫、盆栽澆花水溢出......，全都能夠輕鬆清潔不耗損。除此之外，相較於整體空間設計採用&nbsp;Mikado Quartz&nbsp;帝雉石的成本預算，對於沒有立即裝修需求的顧客來說，by Saiens&nbsp;的設計家飾在價格上親民許多，也能夠先為家中帶來不同的氛圍與設計質感，可說是「家中的第一塊帝雉石」呢！&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</code></pre><pre><code>「Artistry meets Technology.&nbsp;當美學遇見科學。」作為Mikado Quartz&nbsp;帝雉石的品牌精神，by Saiens&nbsp;更是完美融合了美學及科學，讓兩者在居家生活中相遇，在&nbsp;by Saiens，美學與科學才能互為完整。</code></pre></div>\n\n\n  \n<style id=\"container-styles\">#block-c7877b3e4dbd62b79bd5 {\n    \n    --stroke-style: none;--stroke-thickness: 6px;\n    \n      \n      \n      \n    \n\n--tweak-text-block-background-color: initial;\n\n  }\n\n  #block-c7877b3e4dbd62b79bd5 .sqs-html-content {\n    \n    --tweak-text-block-padding: 6% 6% 6% 6%;\n  --tweak-text-block-padding: initial;\n}\n\n  #block-c7877b3e4dbd62b79bd5 {\n      mix-blend-mode: var(--tweak-text-block-blend\n  );\n      border-radius: var(--tweak-text-block-radius);\n  }\n\n  \n  \n#block-c7877b3e4dbd62b79bd5 {\n      --tweak-text-block-radius: 0px 0px 0px 0px;\n    }\n\n\n  \n  \n\n  #block-c7877b3e4dbd62b79bd5 {\n    }\n\n</style>\n\n<style id=\"override-container-styles\">\n    @media screen and (max-width: 767px) {\n          \n            \n\n#block-c7877b3e4dbd62b79bd5 {\n            \n            }\n        }\n    \n  \n    @media screen and (max-width: 767px) {\n          #block-c7877b3e4dbd62b79bd5 .sqs-html-content {\n            \n            }\n        }\n    \n  @media screen and (max-width: 767px) {\n          \n          \n\n          \n          \n          \n        }</style>\n\n<style class=\"transform-overrides-vars\">\n    \n  </style>\n\n\n\n</div>\n</div></div></div></div></div>"
}